'''Ardaranye''' was the [[Quenya]] name for "the '''Kingdom of [[Arda]]'''" under the guardianship and headship of [[Manwë|Manwë Súlimo]], the Elder King of the [[Valar]], which is [[Ambar#Ambar|Ambar]] 'the Earth' as a whole planet (including the [[Aman|Blessed Realm]] until its [[Changing of the World|removal]] from the [[Circles of the World|circles of the world]] after the [[Downfall of Númenor]] in {{SA|3319}}) together with all the celestial objects nearest to it, including the [[Moon]], the [[Sun]], and even some '[[stars]]'.<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 105</ref>

In other words, ''Ardaranye'' was precisely an equivalent for the whole '''[[:Wikipedia:Solar System|Solar System]]'''.

